fulltitle: Christian McBride - The Future of Jazz
description:
Christian McBride’s advocacy for music and music education was born out of a love for playing. In this video, he discusses working with his wife, Melissa Walker, to found Jazz House Kids, an organization that gives young people a chance to experience music in a way they might not be able to without support. He also offers some advice for the future leaders of jazz.

Read the blog: http://blogs.jwpepper.com/index.php/jazz-100-christian-mcbride-and-the-future-of-jazz?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=youtube&utm_campaign=jazz100-blogs&utm_content=mcbride-video2
